name: THē-bo͞oɡēˌman
description:
Welcoming october.

I decided to draw something unusual in this spooky month. Halloween (Serial Killer) Movie inspired illustration, also as my favorite vintage horror stuff.

The main character: Michael Myers, does what he does because he is The Boogeyman, set to remind us all why responsibility and fear are important.

Dim. 4234 x 5319 pixels
